bilingual.source: Many resolutions have to do with self-improvement.
bilingual.target: 许多决心与自我提升有关。

bilingual.source: It is a time for worship, self-control, and meditation.
bilingual.target: 这是一个敬拜、自我控制和冥想的时间。

bilingual.source: People are usually required to give a general self-introduction in a job interview.
bilingual.target: 人们通常需要在工作面试中做一个自我介绍。

bilingual.source: Self-evaluation is a good way to improve self-awareness.
bilingual.target: 自我评价是提高自我意识的好方法。
自爱并不是自私，而是自我关怀。
克服自以为是需要谦逊和自我意识。
自我表达对她来说很重要。

bilingual.source: He has a clear understanding of his self.
bilingual.target: 他对自我的认知很清晰。
他感受到的压力是自我引发的。
自我发展需要时间和努力。

list.abstract: self（[self]），英语单词，作名词为自己；自我；个性。作代词为自己；本人。作形容词为与其他部分同质同色的。作动词为使自花授粉；使自体受精；同系繁殖。短语搭配有self-driving car（无人驾驶汽车）。例句为“More self-driving trucks on the road.（更多的无人驾驶卡车上路。）” self名词类近义词有essence、principle等。形容词类近义词有same、identical。复数为selves。名词形式为selfishness。形容词形式为selfish。副词形式为selfishly。
《self》，陈绮贞演唱歌曲，收录于2005年专辑《华丽的冒险》中。

yingyinNormal.en: You mean because she's self-obsessed, self-serving, self-centered, self... No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说她的自恋自私，自我，自...

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Mastery of chi requires Mastery of self.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢。气的运用需要自我修炼。

yingyinNormal.en: On the contrary. Far be it from me to get in the way of a voyage of self-discovery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恰恰相反，我没有立场去阻碍自我发现之旅。

yingyinNormal.en: Look at me. Why, I've become like all of you, savage, fear-ridden, selfish. An entire town of formerly good citizens turned into heartless freaks, bent on their own self-prever, self-preter...
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看我，我怎么变得和你们一样了。野蛮粗鲁，心惊胆战，自私自利。整个镇的优良市民被变成了没心没肺的怪胎，满脑子都是他们的自我包，自我宝……
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: I think it's a bold step, and I support you in your journey of self-improvement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得你这么做很勇敢，我支持你为自我提升而做出的努力。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, that, right there, that equivocation and self-doubt, that is not the American spirit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就是这种支吾的语气和自我怀疑，这可不是美国精神。

yingyinNormal.en: We developed a mutagen capable of stimulating self-repair on a cellular level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们研发了一种刺激有机体突变的物质，能够在细胞面上自我修复。

yingyinNormal.en: I was spoiled, self-centered. And you guys really took care of me. Yeah. Monica made us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 被惯坏，以自我为中心，你们几个却很照顾我。莫妮强迫我们来着。

yingyinNormal.en: This ship is self-correcting its course. Thing's on autopilot. Can we control it? Fly us home?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这艘船在自我纠正航线。它在自动驾驶。我们能控制它吗？飞回家？

yingyinNormal.en: Of course, we are fickle stupid beings with poor memories and a great gift for self-destruction.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然，我们人类是浮躁，愚蠢的存在，好了伤疤忘了疼，生来就热衷自我毁灭。

yingyinNormal.en: Which leads to a crazy high followed by a tearful, self-loathing crash. It's a Days of Red Vines and Roses.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他每次吃糖吃到嗨到山顶，过后就会飙泪自我厌恶到谷底。简直就是《醉乡情断》的翻版。

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't expect, but I saw Stark's fear, I knew it would could control him, make him self-destruct.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我未曾预料到会是如此，但我看到了史塔克内心的恐惧，我知道他会被这恐惧控制，走向自我毁灭。

yingyinNormal.en: The Singularity. When the system is capable of recursive self-improvement, when it is better at recalibrating, expanding and spawning than we are, the brief blip of humanity's reign will reach its inevitable conclusion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就是奇点，当系统能够实现递归的自我强化，当它能更好地进行自我校准扩张与繁殖速度都超过我们时，人类短暂的统治将不可避免地走到尽头。

yingyinNormal.en: Their lives are blissful. In a way, their existence is purer than ours, freed of the burden of self-doubt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们的生活非常幸福，在某种程度上，他们的生活方式比我们更加纯粹，没有自我怀疑的负担。

yingyinNormal.en: In laymen's terms, yeah. Interesting. So you don't believe there's a Cartesian self that underlies the flux of experience?
yingyinNormal.zh: 用非专业术语来说，是的。有意思。所以你不认为有个笛卡尔自我在经历流之下吗？

yingyinNormal.en: So you're proposing that the self is an illusion, and that we actually have multiple centers of consciousness that are communicating with one another?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你是在说自我只是幻觉，人其实有多个意识中心它们在相互交流吗？

yingyinNormal.en: If there's a silence then turned that into a joke. Stay natural, self-facing and the audience will be on your side. Let's recap.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果观众不笑，就当作自我解嘲。保持自然，忠实呈现自我这样观众就会喜欢你了。再复习一遍！
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《公开场合演讲如何展现自信？》

yingyinNormal.en: As you know, my brother has embarked on a programme of self-destruction remarkable even by his standards, and I am endeavouring to find out what triggered it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如你所知，我弟弟走上了决绝的自我毁灭之路，就他而言也很严重，我正在努力找出诱因。

yingyinNormal.en: I have come to think of so much of consciousness as a burden, a weight, and we have spared them that. Anxiety, self-loathing, guilt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我逐渐开始认为，意识过剩是一种负担，太过沉重，我们必须将他们身上多余的去除，忧虑，自我憎恨，愧疚。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know. I thought Trump would self-destruct, so what do I know? Primaries are their own insanity. What are you making?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不知道，我还觉得特朗普[美国本届候选人]会自我毁灭呢，我怎么觉得有什么用？初选就是他们自个儿在那儿胡闹，你调的什么？

examination_example.sentence: According to the last paragraph, a key to coping with dark patterns is businesses' <highlight>self</highlight>-discipline.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据最后一段，应对黑暗模式的关键是企业的自律。

examination_example.sentence: Some people argue that food <highlight>self</highlight>-sufficiency in the UK would post a challenge to its farming industry.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一些人认为，英国的粮食自给自足将对其农业构成挑战。

examination_example.sentence: A move back to <highlight>self</highlight>-sufficiency, the argument goes, would boost the farming industry, political sovereignty and even the nation's health.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有观点认为，回归自给自足将促进农业、政治主权甚至国家的健康。

examination_example.sentence: They transform the aspirations of the people who live there; they nudge the <highlight>self</highlight>-image of the city into a bolder and more optimistic light.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它们改变了当地居民的愿望; 他们推使城市的自我形象变得更加大胆、更加乐观。

examination_example.sentence: And interest groups exert <highlight>self</highlight>-interested pressure on the USPs's ultimate overseer — Congress.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 利益团体为了自己的利益，给美国邮政管理局的最后的监管者--国会--施加了压力。

examination_example.sentence: The oldest tends to be <highlight>self-assured</highlight>, responsible, a high achiever, and relatively serious and reserved.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 年龄最大的人往往很自信，有责任感，成就高，并且相对严肃和内向。

examination_example.sentence: They tend to be <highlight>self-assured</highlight> and responsible.

examination_example.sentence: There's no question that <highlight>self-driving</highlight> vehicles could be an enormous benefit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毫无疑问，自动驾驶汽车可以带来巨大的好处。

examination_example.sentence: 60% of drivers would like to get some kind of <highlight>self-driving</highlight> feature, such as automatic braking or self-parking.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 60%的司机希望获得某种自动驾驶功能，如自动刹车或自动泊车。

examination_example.sentence: His solution was to learn something from the rebels it was fighting: decentralize authority to <highlight>self</highlight>-organizing teams.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他的解决方案是从与之战斗的叛军那里学到一些东西：将权力下放给自组织团队。

examination_example.sentence: Parents often praise, believing they are building their child's <highlight>self-confidence</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 父母经常表扬孩子，认为这样可以培养孩子的自信心。

examination_example.sentence: Researching this phenomenon, another team asked volunteers to watch boring, sad, or neutral films, during which they could <highlight>self</highlight>-administer electric shocks.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在研究这一现象时，另一个团队要求志愿者观看无聊、悲伤或中性的电影，在此期间他们可以自我实施电击。

examination_example.sentence: We found no relationship between the average person's <highlight>self</highlight>-perception of weight and labor market outcomes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们发现普通人对体重的自我认知与劳动力市场结果之间没有关系。

examination_example.sentence: Self-perceived weight can influence <highlight>self-esteem</highlight> (自尊心) , mental health and health behaviors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自我感知的体重会影响自尊心、心理健康和健康行为。

examination_example.sentence: I'm <highlight>self</highlight>-employed, which means I work for myself and I do what I love.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我是自由职业者，这意味着我为自己工作，做我热爱的事情。

examination_example.sentence: Those who were more <highlight>self</highlight>-disciplined, for instance, were no more likely to live to be very old.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，那些更自律的人活到很老的可能性并不会更大。

examination_example.sentence: In short, <highlight>self</highlight> protection is important to us.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 简而言之，自我保护对我们很重要。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Self</highlight> — fit course: studying at your own pace ．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自选课程：按照自己的节奏学习。

examination_example.sentence: The advantage of "<highlight>self</highlight> — fit course" is that you may choose your own.
examination_example.sentence_trans: "自选课程"的好处是你可以选择你自己的课程。
